{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":995,"text":"In the next six minutes\nthat you will listen to me,"},{"time":4968,"text":"the world will have lost three mothers"},{"time":7529,"text":"while delivering their babies:"},{"time":10591,"text":"one, because of a severe complication;"},{"time":14501,"text":"second, because she will be a teenager"},{"time":17043,"text":"and her body will not\nbe prepared for birth;"},{"time":20852,"text":"but the third, only because of lack\nof access to basic clean tools"},{"time":26882,"text":"at the time of childbirth."},{"time":29676,"text":"She will not be alone."},{"time":31983,"text":"Over one million mothers and babies\ndie every single year"},{"time":35682,"text":"in the developing world,"},{"time":37235,"text":"only because of lack of access\nto basic cleanliness"},{"time":41003,"text":"while giving birth to their babies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":44781,"text":"My journey began on a hot summer afternoon"},{"time":47283,"text":"in India in 2008,"},{"time":49475,"text":"when after a day of meeting women\nand listening to their needs,"},{"time":53172,"text":"I landed in a thatched hut with a midwife."},{"time":57035,"text":"As a mother, I was very curious\non how she delivered babies in her house."},{"time":61809,"text":"After a deep and engaging\nconversation with her"},{"time":64536,"text":"on how she considered it a profound\ncalling to do what she was doing,"},{"time":68906,"text":"I asked her a parting question:"},{"time":71581,"text":"Do you have the tools that you need\nto deliver the babies?"},{"time":75941,"text":"I got to see her tool."},{"time":78599,"text":"\"This is what I use to separate\nthe mother and the baby,\" she said."},{"time":83800,"text":"Unsure of how to react, I held this\nagricultural tool in my hand in shock."},{"time":89644,"text":"I took a picture of this,\nhugged her and walked away."},{"time":93640,"text":"My mind was flooded with reflections\nof my own infection"},{"time":96633,"text":"that I had to struggle with\nfor a year past childbirth"},{"time":99689,"text":"despite having access\nto the best medical care,"},{"time":103263,"text":"and memories of my conversation\nwith my father,"},{"time":105669,"text":"who had lost his mom to childbirth,"},{"time":107858,"text":"on how he thought his life\nwould be so different"},{"time":110324,"text":"if she would have been\njust next to him growing up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":113812,"text":"As a product developer,\nI started my process of research."},{"time":117593,"text":"I was very excited to find\nthat there was a product out there"},{"time":120792,"text":"called the Clean Birth Kit."},{"time":122830,"text":"But I just couldn't buy one for months."},{"time":126211,"text":"They were only assembled\nbased on availability of funding."},{"time":130998,"text":"Finally, when I got my hands on one,\nI was in shock again."},{"time":134963,"text":"I would never use these tools\nto deliver my baby, I thought."},{"time":138653,"text":"But to confirm my instincts,\nI went back to the women,"},{"time":141588,"text":"some of whom had the experience\nof using this product."}]},{"cues":[{"time":145496,"text":"Lo and behold, they had\nthe same reaction and more."},{"time":149022,"text":"The women said they would rather\ndeliver on a floor"},{"time":151556,"text":"than on a plastic sheet\nthat smeared blood all over."},{"time":154178,"text":"They were absolutely right --\nit would cause more infection."},{"time":157617,"text":"The thread provided was a highway\nto bacterial infection"},{"time":160650,"text":"through the baby's umbilical cord,"},{"time":162373,"text":"and the blade used was the kind\nthat men used for shaving,"},{"time":165241,"text":"and they did not want it\nanywhere close to them."},{"time":168629,"text":"There was no incentive for anybody\nto redesign this product,"},{"time":171607,"text":"because it was based on charity."},{"time":173542,"text":"The women were never\nconsulted in this process."},{"time":176884,"text":"And to my surprise, the need\nwas not only in homes"},{"time":179407,"text":"but also in institutional settings\nwith high-volume births."},{"time":182760,"text":"Situations in remote areas\nwere even more daunting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":186629,"text":"This had to change."},{"time":188229,"text":"I made this my area of focus."},{"time":190515,"text":"I started the design process\nby collecting feedback,"},{"time":194591,"text":"developing prototypes"},{"time":196030,"text":"and engaging with various stakeholders\nresearching global protocols."},{"time":200306,"text":"With every single prototype,\nwe went back to the women"},{"time":202972,"text":"to ensure that we had a product for them."},{"time":206049,"text":"What I learned through this process\nwas that these women,"},{"time":208799,"text":"despite their extreme poverty,"},{"time":210262,"text":"placed great value\non their health and well-being."},{"time":212663,"text":"They were absolutely not poor in mind."},{"time":215137,"text":"As with all of us, they would appreciate\na well-designed product"},{"time":218162,"text":"developed for their needs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":220250,"text":"After many iterations\nworking with experts,"},{"time":222771,"text":"medical health professionals"},{"time":224276,"text":"and the women themselves,"},{"time":226135,"text":"I should say it was not\nan easy process at all,"},{"time":229527,"text":"but we had a simple and beautiful design."},{"time":233687,"text":"For a dollar more than what\nthe existing product was offered for,"},{"time":238481,"text":"at three dollars, we were able\nto deliver \"janma,\""},{"time":241256,"text":"a clean birth kit in a purse."},{"time":244058,"text":"Janma, meaning \"birth,\" contained\na blood-absorbing sheet"},{"time":246902,"text":"for the woman to give birth on,"},{"time":248653,"text":"a surgical scalpel, a cord clamp,\na bar of soap, a pair of gloves"},{"time":252682,"text":"and the first cloth\nto wipe the baby clean."},{"time":255369,"text":"All this came packaged\nin a beautiful purse"},{"time":257581,"text":"that was given to the mother\nas a gift after all her hard work,"},{"time":260820,"text":"that she carried home with pride\nas a symbol of prosperity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":265865,"text":"One woman reacted to this gift."},{"time":268347,"text":"She said, \"Is this really mine?\nCan I keep it?\""},{"time":272095,"text":"The other one said,\n\"Will you give me a different color"},{"time":274728,"text":"when I have my next baby?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":276231,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":278009,"text":"Better yet, a woman expressed\nthat this was the first purse"},{"time":280950,"text":"that she had ever owned in her life."},{"time":283051,"text":"The kit, aside from its symbolism\nand its simplicity,"},{"time":285859,"text":"is designed to follow\nglobally recommended medical protocol"},{"time":289195,"text":"and serves as a behavior-change tool\nto follow steps one after the other."},{"time":294098,"text":"It can not only be used in homes,\nbut also in institutional settings."}]},{"cues":[{"time":298656,"text":"To date, our kit has impacted\nover 600,000 mothers and babies"},{"time":302629,"text":"around the world."},{"time":304401,"text":"It's a humbling experience\nto watch these numbers grow,"},{"time":307668,"text":"and I cannot wait until\nwe reach a hundred million."}]},{"cues":[{"time":312879,"text":"But women's health issues do not end here."},{"time":315777,"text":"There are thousands of simple issues\nthat require low-cost interventions."},{"time":319811,"text":"We have facts to prove\nthat if we invest in women and girls"},{"time":322751,"text":"and provide them with better\nhealth and well-being,"},{"time":325184,"text":"they will deliver healthier and wealthier\nand prosperous communities."},{"time":330219,"text":"We have to start by bringing simplicity\nand dignity to women's health issues:"},{"time":334227,"text":"from reducing maternal mortality,\nto breaking taboos,"},{"time":337323,"text":"to empowering women\nto take control of their own lives."},{"time":340857,"text":"This is my dream."},{"time":343317,"text":"But it is not possible to achieve it\nwithout engaging men and women alike"},{"time":347797,"text":"from around the world --"},{"time":349262,"text":"yes, all of you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":352773,"text":"I recently heard this lyric\nby Leonard Cohen:"},{"time":356962,"text":"\"Ring the bells that still can ring."},{"time":360209,"text":"Forget your perfect offering."},{"time":363373,"text":"There is a crack in everything."},{"time":366298,"text":"That's how the light gets in.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":369070,"text":"This is my bit of light."},{"time":371541,"text":"But we need more light."},{"time":373209,"text":"In fact, we need huge spotlights\nplaced in the world of women's health"},{"time":376677,"text":"if we need a better tomorrow."},{"time":378999,"text":"We should never forget that women\nare at the center of a sustainable world,"},{"time":383516,"text":"and we do not exist without them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":386067,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":387250,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}